      "text": "No new keys here - just flow. You'll loop one short word over and over until your fingers fire without you asking them to. Flow, not force."
    },
    {
      "type": "drop",
      "text": "Eyes off the keys, hands settled on home row. Repeat each word at a single even pace - same gap between every tap. Don't rush it, hold the beat steady the whole way."
